      %section
        %h1 About McKinsey Academy
        %p McKinsey Academy helps rising professionals advance their careers by providing distinctive learning experiences taught by distinguished practitioners on a global digital platform. McKinsey Academy helps clients rapidly build capability and improve individual effectiveness and corporate performance.
      %hr
      %section
        .sub-1 what is mckinsey academy?
        %p.what-is McKinsey Academy prepares rising professionals for the next step in their careers through practitioner-led learning immediately applicable in the workplace.
      %section
        %p McKinsey Academy is a premium digital platform for professional education. We empower leaders and business professionals to build the skills, knowledge, and capabilities to enhance individual effectiveness for improved corporate performance.
      %section
        %p.style-2 How we work
        %p McKinsey Academy courses are developed by distinguished practitioners and industry experts who share their insights and experience across key business topics. We use emerging learning tools and formats, and digital collaboration techniques to improve individual effectiveness and corporate performance.
      %section
        %ul.info
          %li Digital delivery using cutting-edge learning techniques
          %li Created and convened by McKinsey partners from a practitioner’s perspective
          %li Tailored for busy professionals
          %li Collaborative and adaptive learning techniques
          %li Global, multi-industry cohorts
          %li Programs and individual courses
          %li McKinsey teaching assistant guidance
      %section
        %p Education is moving fundamentally, rapidly, and inexorably to digital delivery, but business management and executive education programs have failed to adapt. In fact, many companies are reducing investment in training even as it becomes more critical. McKinsey Academy was created to help address the professional development needs of companies:
      %section
        %ul.info
          %li How to get value from employees starting on day one
          %li How to accelerate capability building for rising professionals
          %li How to provide continuous professional development to attract and retain the best employees
